(Executive Summary) Tj
T*
(- Block time: 120 seconds \(262,800 blocks/year\).) Tj
T*
(- Era size: 2,000,000 blocks \(~7.61 years\).) Tj
T*
(- Eight pre-tail eras: 100 -> 50 -> 25 -> 12.5 -> 6.25 -> 3.125 -> 1.5625 -> 0.78125 ATHO/block.) Tj
T*
(- Bootstrap allocation: 781,250 ATHO at block 1 \(included in total pre-tail base\).) Tj
T*
(- Tail starts at height 17,000,000 \(~64.69 years\) at 0.1953125 ATHO/block.) Tj
T*
(- Tail annual issuance: 51,328.125 ATHO/year.) Tj
T*
(- Hard max supply cap: 500,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Fee floor: 500 atoms/vB \(5e-7 ATHO/vB\).) Tj
T*
(- Fee routing: pre-tail 40% to consensus pool, post-tail 55% to consensus pool.) Tj
T*
(- Tail burn target on non-pool share: 100% burn / 0% miner, with floor clipping.) Tj
T*
(- Supply floor: 21,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Protocol deflation threshold: ~24.802% sustained utilization.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
